videos.headline: Back-to-back fumbles create early excitement between PSU & OSU
videos.description: Jeremey Ruckert gets the ball stripped and recovered by Penn State's Ji'Ayir Brown. Marcus Williamson then forces Noah Cain to fumble on the next play and Ohio State recovers.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Back-to-back fumbles create early excitement between PSU & OSU) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sean Clifford finds Brenton Strange for a Penn State TD
videos.description: Sean Clifford rolls to his right and darts a pass through traffic to Brenton Strange to score a 5-yard touchdown for Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sean Clifford finds Brenton Strange for a Penn State TD) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Buckeyes take their first lead on Chris Olave's TD catch
videos.description: C.J. Stroud throws a deep pass to Chris Olave to score a 38-yard touchdown to give Ohio State a 10-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buckeyes take their first lead on Chris Olave's TD catch) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Big-man TD! Jerron Cage takes fumble recover 57 yards
videos.description: Sean Clifford fumbles the football and Jerron Cage scoops it up and chugs his way to the end zone for a 57-yard scoop-and-score for Ohio State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Big-man TD! Jerron Cage takes fumble recover 57 yards) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jahan Dotson dives for Penn State TD
videos.description: Jahan Dotson takes the direct snap and stretches out for the pylon as he is hit out of bounds to score a 2-yard touchdown to tie the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jahan Dotson dives for Penn State TD) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: TreVeyon Henderson's TD extends Ohio State's lead
videos.description: TreVeyon Henderson takes the handoff and battles his way across the goal line to score a 1-yard touchdown to give Ohio State a 27-17 lead over Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (TreVeyon Henderson's TD extends Ohio State's lead) 2021/10/30 EHSEET
